                        &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                        PORTADOR DE DEFICIÊNCIA FÍSICA E / OU VISUAL
                    </p>
                    <div class="card">
                        <p>
                            &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                            &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                            <b>IDENTIFICAÇÃO DO REQUERENTE</b>
                            <br />
                            &emsp;&emsp;Nome:&emsp;@Html.DisplayFor(model => model.Nome)
                            &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                            &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                            &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                            CPF:&emsp;@Html.DisplayFor(model => model.CPF)
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <p>
                            &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                            &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                            <u><b>PORTADOR DE DEFICIÊNCIA FÍSICA</b></u>
                            <br />
                            &emsp;&emsp;
                            O interessado acima identificado foi submetido a perícia perante esta Junta Médica, onde constatou-se que, para fins de
                            aquisição de veiculo com <b><u>ISENÇÃO DE IPI</u></b>,
                            <br />
                            &emsp;&emsp;
                            o mesmo <b>É PORTADOR DE DEFICIÊNCIA FISICA</b>, apresentando alteraçãocompleta ou parcial do(s) seguinte(s) <u><b>SEGMENTOS</b></u> do corpo humano:
                            <hr />
                            &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                            &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                            ( Assinalar ao menos um dos segmentos abaixo )
                        </p>
                        &emsp;&emsp;
                        [&emsp;&emsp;]&emsp;CABEÇA&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                        [&emsp;&emsp;]&emsp;PESCOÇO&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                        [&emsp;&emsp;]&emsp;TRONCO&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                        [&emsp;&emsp;]&emsp;MEMBROS INFERIORES&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                        [&emsp;&emsp;]&emsp;MEMBROS SUPERIORES
                        <hr />

                        <p>
                            &emsp;&emsp;
                            A(s) alteração(oes) acima &ensp;ACARRETAM O COMPROMETIMENTO&ensp; DA FUNÇÃO&ensp; FISICA DO&ensp; <b>SEGMENTO</b> AFETADO, &ensp;REPRESENTANDO UMA &ensp;PERDA OU
                            <br />
                            &emsp;&emsp;
                            ANORMALIDADE&ensp; QUE GERA <u><b>INCAPACIDADE</b></u> (*) &ensp;PARA O DESEMPENHO DE ATIVIADE, <b>
                                DENTRO&ensp; DO PADRÃO CONSIDERADO NORMAL PARA&ensp; O SER
                                <br />
                                &emsp; &ensp;
                                HUMANO
                            </b>, ainda que de forma parcial, APRESENTANDO-SE SOB A FORMA DE:
                            <hr />
                            &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                            &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                            ( Assinalar ao menos um dos segmentos abaixo )
                        </p>
                        &emsp;&emsp;
                        [&emsp;&emsp;]&ensp;PARAPLEGIA &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                        [&emsp;&emsp;]&ensp;MONOPARESIA&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                        [&emsp;&emsp;]&ensp;TRIPLEGIA  &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                        [&emsp;&emsp;]&ensp;HEMIPARESIA&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                        [&emsp;&emsp;]&ensp;PARALISIA CEREBRAL
                        <br />
                        &emsp;&emsp;
                        [&emsp;&emsp;]&ensp;PARAPARESIA&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&ensp;
                        [&emsp;&emsp;]&ensp;TETRAPLEGIA&ensp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                        [&emsp;&emsp;]&ensp;TRIPARESIA &ensp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                        [&emsp;&emsp;]&ensp;OSTOMIA &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                        [&emsp;&emsp;]&ensp;NANISMO
                        <br />
                        &emsp;&emsp;
                        [&emsp;&emsp;]&ensp;MONOPLEGIA &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&ensp;
                        [&emsp;&emsp;]&ensp;TETRAPARESIA&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                        [&emsp;&emsp;]&ensp;HEMIPLEGIA &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                        [&emsp;&emsp;]&ensp;AMPUTAÇÃO OU AUSÊNCIA DE MEMBRO


                        <hr />
                        <p>
                            &emsp;&emsp;[&emsp;&emsp;]&emsp;
                            Membros &ensp;Inferiores e/ou &ensp;Superiores com <b><u>DEFORMIDADE&ensp; CONGÊNITA&ensp;</u></b> ou <b><u>ADQUIRIDA</u></b>
                            , sendo que tal deformidade <b>NÃO É DE ORIGEM ESTÉTICA</b>
                            <br />
                            &emsp;&emsp;
                            e resulta em <b>DIFICULDADE</b>
                            para o desempenho&ensp; das funções do <b>MEMBRO</b> deformado, <b>
                                REPRESENTANDO UMA&ensp; PERDA OU ANORMALIDADE&ensp; QUE GERA
                                <br />
                                &ensp;&ensp;&ensp;
                                <u>INCAPACIDADE</u> (*) PARA O DESEMPENHO DE ATIVIDADE, DENTRO DO PADRÃO CONSIDERADO NORMAL PARA O SER HUMANO
                            </b>, ainda &ensp;que de forma
                            <br />
                            &ensp;&ensp;&ensp;
                            parcial.
                            <hr />
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            &emsp;&emsp;
                            <b>(*) INCAPACIDADE </b>- uma <b><u>REDUÇÃO EFETIVA E ACENTUADA</u></b> DA CAPACIDADE DE INTEGRAÇÃO SOCIAL, com necessidade de equipamentos,
                            adaptações,<br />
                            &emsp;&emsp;
                            meios ou recursos&ensp; especiais para que a &ensp;pessoa portadora de&ensp; deficiência possa receber ou transmitir &ensp;informações necessárias ao seu
                            bem-estar pessoal e ao
                            <br />
                            &emsp;&emsp;
                            adaptações, desempenho de função ou atividade a ser exercida. (Dec.3.298/99, art.3º, inc.III).
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <p>
                            &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                            &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                            <u><b>PORTADOR DE DEFICIÊNCIA VISUAL</b></u>
                            <br />
                            &emsp;&emsp;
                            O interessado acima identificado foi submetido a perícia perante esta Junta Médica, onde constatou-se que, para fins de
                            aquisição de veiculo com <b><u>ISENÇÃO DE IPI</u></b>,
                            <br />
                            &emsp;&emsp;
                            o interessado <b><u>É PORTADOR DE DEFICIÊNCIA VISUAL</u></b>, posto que se enquadra na(s) seguinte(s) condição(ões):
                            <hr />

                            &emsp;&emsp;
                            [&emsp;&emsp;]&ensp;Acuidade visual igual ou menor que 20/200 no melhor olho, após a melhor correção. &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&ensp;
                            [&emsp;&emsp;]&ensp;Campo visual inferior a 20° (tabela de Snellen).

                            <hr />

                            &emsp;&emsp;
                            As informações acima fazem parte integrante do Laudo de Avaliação - DEFICIÊNCIA FISICA E/OU VISUAL, Anexo IX da IN RFB 988, de 2009, por nós subscrita,
                            <br />
                            &emsp;&emsp;
                            sendo a expressão da verdade, sob as penas da Lei nº 8137/1990, que trata dos CRIMES CONTRA A ORDEM  TRIBUTÁRIA, combinado com as demais sanções
                            <br />
                            &emsp;&emsp;
                            legais, em especial o disposto no art. 299 do Código Penal.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <p></p>
                    <div class="card-group">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    <br />
                                    <br />
                                    ______________________________________<br />
                                    DR(A). @ViewBag.Med1Nome <br />
                                    CRM: @ViewBag.Med1CRM<br />
                                    Port.Detran: @ViewBag.Med1Port<br />
                                    @ViewBag.Med1Espec<br />
                                    Aut.Especial Port: @ViewBag.Med1Aut<br />
                                    CPF: @ViewBag.Med1CPF
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    <br />
                                    <br />
                                    ______________________________________<br />
                                    DR(A). @ViewBag.Med2Nome <br />
                                    CRM: @ViewBag.Med2CRM<br />
                                    Port.Detran: @ViewBag.Med2Port<br />
                                    @ViewBag.Med2Espec<br />
                                    Aut.Especial Port: @ViewBag.Med2Aut<br />
                                    CPF: @ViewBag.Med2CPF
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;UNIDADE EMISSORA DO LAUDO<br />
                                    ______________________________________<br />
                                    @ViewBag.UnidEmissora<br />
                                    CNPJ: @ViewBag.UnidCnpjf<br /><br />
                                    ______________________________________<br /><br />
                                    &emsp;&emsp;
                                    ________________________________<br />
                                    &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;UEL-Assinatura do Responsável

                                </p>

                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p>
                    &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                    &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
                    Aprovado pela IN RFB nº 1.369, de 2013.
                </p>
            </div>
            <a asp-action="Index" class="glyphicon glyphicon-minus-sign"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
            @*<a asp-action="" class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;*@
            <a asp-action="" onClick="window.print()" class="glyphicon glyphicon-print"></a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- The Modal -->
<div class="modal fade" id="myModal">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-xl">
        <div class="modal-content">

            <!-- Modal Header -->
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h4 class="modal-title">Editar Rodapé do Formulário</h4>
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
            </div>

            <!-- Modal body -->
            @using (Html.BeginForm("EditEntrevistaPCD", "Cliente", FormMethod.Post))
            {                
                <input name="Id" type="hidden" value="@Html.DisplayFor(model => model.Id)" />
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <div class="card-group">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    DR(A).            <input name="Medico1" type="text" value="@ViewBag.Med1Nome" style="border:1px solid #DCDCDC"><br />
                                    CRM:              <input name="CRM1" type="text" value="@ViewBag.Med1CRM" style="border:1px solid #DCDCDC"><br />
                                    Port.Detran:      <input name="Port1" type="text" value="@ViewBag.Med1Port" style="border:1px solid #DCDCDC"><br />
                                    Especialidade:    <input name="Espec1" type="text" value="@ViewBag.Med1Espec" style="border:1px solid #DCDCDC"><br />
                                    Aut.Especial Port:<input name="Aut1" type="text" value="@ViewBag.Med1Aut" style="border:1px solid #DCDCDC"><br />
                                    CPF:              <input name="CPF1" type="text" value="@ViewBag.Med1CPF" style="border:1px solid #DCDCDC"><br />
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    DR(A).            <input name="Medico2" type="text" value="@ViewBag.Med2Nome" style="border:1px solid #DCDCDC"><br />
                                    CRM:              <input name="CRM2" type="text" value="@ViewBag.Med2CRM" style="border:1px solid #DCDCDC"><br />
                                    Port.Detran:      <input name="Port2" type="text" value="@ViewBag.Med2Port" style="border:1px solid #DCDCDC"><br />
                                    Especialidade:    <input name="Espec2" type="text" value="@ViewBag.Med2Espec" style="border:1px solid #DCDCDC"><br />
                                    Aut.Especial Port:<input name="Aut2" type="text" value="@ViewBag.Med2Aut" style="border:1px solid #DCDCDC"><br />
                                    CPF:              <input name="CPF2" type="text" value="@ViewBag.Med2CPF" style="border:1px solid #DCDCDC"><br />
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    POSTO: <input name="Posto" type="text" value="@ViewBag.UnidEmissora" style="border:1px solid #DCDCDC"><br />
                                    CNPJ: <input name="Cnpj" type="text" value="@ViewBag.UnidCnpjf" style="border:1px solid #DCDCDC">
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Modal footer -->
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <input type="submit" value="Salvar" class="btn btn-primary" />
                </div>
            }
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
